{"tid":2427569,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺 褶被 有個習字好唔識避諱","createTime":"2021-03-01T01:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T01:57:41.000Z","uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19e9abcac334849e47a72e0f80369ee27e2dfdc8","tid":2427569,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T01:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3d79b31b153677bf1198c0bc9e50a242f8bc08","tid":2427569,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E7%A4%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-mf%2Fsearch.php%3Fword%3D%25E7%25A4%25BA&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3ZFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=e6a02d72\" target=\"_blank\">https://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-mf/search.php?word=%E7%A4%BA</a><br />\n略說: 甲金文象神主牌位之形。<br />\n11 字<br />\n 詳解: 關於「示」字之釋形說法甚多，未有定論。一說認為設杆以祭天，以象徵神祇(丁山)。二說象神主牌位形，如徐中舒：「象以木表或石柱為神主之形。」「示」下數點象祭祀拜禱時灌酒之狀(姚孝遂)。沒有數點之「示」與「主」初本同字，後分化為二，甲骨文表示神主，又用為祭名。參見「主」。<br />\n<br />\n  金文皆用作人名、族氏名。在簡帛文獻中，「示」多寫作「視」，表示顯示，《馬王堆．老子甲本》：「邦利器不可以視人」，《老子乙本》作「邦利器不可以示人」，「視」、「示」古韻相同，《漢書》亦多以「視」為「示」，古字通用。<br />\n<br />\n  《說文》：「天垂象，見吉凶，所以示人也。从二。(二，古文上字。)三垂，日月星也。觀乎天文，以察時變。示，神事也。凡示之屬皆从示。𥘅，古文示。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">祭祀習, 乃大不敬之罪, 所有公司名有&quot;<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">褶</span></strong>&quot;字既都違反國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>我要報國安等你班反中亂港既仆街腦細全部坐監</strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"47e29c1cc984e23ddcf11a7e7353056ce9f8a4bb","tid":2427569,"uid":34912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T01:57:41.000Z","msg":"幾時褶埋？"}]}